sentences: Nanase Aikawa (相川 七瀬, Aikawa Nanase, born February 16, 1975) is a Japanese rock and pop singer.
Nanase Aikawa was born on February 16, 1975, in Osaka, Japan.
Throughout her school years, Nanase had sung and participated in several singing competitions.
At the age of 20 she released her first single, Yume Miru Shoujo ja Irarenai on November 8, 1995.
